                    </div>
                    <div class="service-item">
                        <h3>Fast and Friendly</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted">Our system is designed for speed and simplicity, delivering rapid responses to meet your needs. With an intuitive and user-friendly interface, we make it easy for you to navigate and utilize our tools, ensuring a seamless experience.</p>
                    </div>
